---
// Warning banner shown when location is from cache (stale GPS data).
// Hidden by default; shown/hidden by app.ts via `location:source-changed`.
---
<div
  id="location-disclaimer"
  class="hidden mx-4 mt-4 p-3 bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-950 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800 rounded-lg text-sm text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200"
  role="status"
  data-i18n="location.cachedWarning"
>
  Using your last known location. Prayer times and Qibla direction may be inaccurate if you've moved since your last visit.
</div>
